	(text "USB Hardware Design Guidelines for FTDI ICs p8 -> 10nF Cap + Ferrite Bead + 100nF Cap + 4.7uF Cap\nI disregarded such heavy filtering for the easier to implement 1uF and 100nF cap given in the CP2102 datasheet\n"
